7:24:53Z. Please identify the root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-13 07:10:53+00:00 to 2025-06-13 07:24:53+00:00"}, "log_data_collected": true, "log_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"latency\", \"AdService-getRandomAds\", \"Transformer\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Latency issue detected in AdService component, related to the method AdService-getRandomAds\",\n      \"evidence\": \"org.jboss.byteman.agent.Transformer: possible trigger for rule AdService-getRandomAds-latency-1749798653 in class hipstershop.AdService\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Trigger point inserted in AdService method, indicating latency rule activation\",\n      \"evidence\": \"RuleTriggerMethodAdapter.injectTriggerPoint: inserting trigger into hipstershop.AdService.getRandomAds() java.util.List for rule AdService-getRandomAds-latency-1749798653\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Trigger inserted confirming rule activation on latency for method AdService-getRandomAds\",\n      \"evidence\": \"org.jboss.byteman.agent.Transformer: inserted trigger for AdService-getRandomAds-latency-1749798653 in class hipstershop.AdService\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "trace_analysis_findings": "根据调用链数据的分析，我们可以识别出以下异常调用链和相关问题：\n\n### 异常调用链分析\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\",\n    \"frontend->cartservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"latency_spike\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Normal Avg Duration: 1739.74, Anomaly Avg Duration: 40034.5, Occurrence: 1\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"latency_spike in redis affecting cartservice\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Normal Avg Duration: 3785.52, Anomaly Avg Duration: 25458.125, Occurrence: 2\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"latency_spike due to downstream cartservice delay\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Normal Avg Duration: 5216.28, Anomaly Avg Duration: 26954.75, Occurrence: 2\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"latency_spike during shipping request\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Normal Avg Duration: 8453.27, Anomaly Avg Duration: 19683.33, Occurrence: 1\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"latency_spike\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Normal Avg Duration: 217.23, Anomaly Avg Duration: 783.0, Occurrence: 1\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 关键发现\n- **Redis** 服务在被调用时，异常耗时显著增加，可能引起 CartService 的延迟。\n- **CartService** 在调用 Redis 服务时，异常耗时显著增加，进而影响到前端服务。\n- **CheckoutService** 在调用 ShippingService 时也出现显著延迟。\n- **ShippingService** 也出现了一定程度的延迟，可能与 CheckoutService 的请求负载有关。\n\n### 结论\n多个服务的延迟可能与 **Redis** 服务的响应时间异常相关联，这是最有可能的根因。可以推测，这些延迟会导致下游服务与最终用户的请求出现显著滞后。建议重点关注 Redis 服务的健康状态和负载处理能力。", "metric_analysis_findings": "根据提供的异常指标数据，我们对故障期间进行了全面分析。以下是显著的异常调用链和分析结果：\n\n### 检测到的异常指标\n我们提取了所有显著变化的指标，选择变化率绝对值最大的Top 3指标如下：\n- `rrt_max` (在多个服务上出现变化)\n- `node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes`\n- `node_memory_usage_rate`\n\n### 异常分析和假设\n- **Component**: \"aiops-k8s-08\"\n  - **Reason**: \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes and node_memory_usage_rate both showed significant degradation indicating memory exhaustion causing downstream performance degradation in pods/containers.\"\n  - **Evidence**: \"Node aiops-k8s-08's memory availability dropped from 12399329280 bytes to 9624905728 bytes and memory usage rate increased from 38.11% to 55.98%.\"\n\n- **Component**: \"currencyservice\"\n  - **Reason**: \"Service rrt_max increased significantly, likely due to memory pressure on nodes impacting service latency.\"\n  - **Evidence**: \"For currencyservice, rrt_max increased from 2362.0 to 2119.5 with median_change_ratio of 0.1082 and p99_change_ratio of 1.4222.\"\n\n- **Component**: \"adservice\"\n  - **Reason**: \"Service rrt_max increased as a symptom of node memory issues.\"\n  - **Evidence**: \"For adservice, rrt_max increased from 5187.0 to 39007.5 with a median change ratio of 1.5305.\"\n\n### JSON 输出\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\", \"node_memory_usage_rate\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-08\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes and node_memory_usage_rate both showed significant degradation indicating memory exhaustion causing downstream performance degradation in pods/containers.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Node aiops-k8s-08's memory availability dropped from 12399329280 bytes to 9624905728 bytes and memory usage rate increased from 38.11% to 55.98%.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Service rrt_max increased significantly, likely due to memory pressure on nodes impacting service latency.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"For currencyservice, rrt_max increased from 2362.0 to 2119.5 with median_change_ratio of 0.1082 and p99_change_ratio of 1.4222.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Service rrt_max increased as a symptom of node memory issues.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"For adservice, rrt_max increased from 5187.0 to 39007.5 with a median change ratio of 1.5305.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n通过对数据指标进行深入分析，我们发现Node aiops-k8s-08的内存耗尽情况是导致相关服务出现性能 degradation的根本原因。请进一步调查该节点的内存配置和Pod分布情况以缓解此故障。"}
